{ xdg-utils

  Utilities to manage → development/web/Multipurpose-Internet-Mail-Extensions[MIME types].

  → Linux/shell/commands/xdg/mime,
  → Linux/shell/commands/xdg-open

  { Debugging xdg-utils

code {
$ export XDG_UTILS_DEBUG_LEVEL=10
$ xdg-open …
code }

  }

}

